description: Reference libraries for Project Arrhythmia modding
releaseNotes:
# 24.8.5 [alpha]
*QOL improvement update focused on UI / UX in menus.*

## Features
- New arcade saves file generated.
- New [recent] arcade sorting option. This allows you to sort by most recently played levels. (replaces old [bpm] option)

## Improvements
- Minor Main Menu UI tweaks.
- Add in page swap noise to arcade menus.
- Several minor UI / UX improvements for arcade menus.
- Using the left and right buttons on the page selector at the bottom now no longer snap your selection up on page swap. 

## Changes
- Recent sorting is now on by default.

## Fixes
- Player should no longer get stuck after dying in some cases.
- Rank sorting in arcade should now work correctly.

# [Alpha] -> [Default]
This build is a release candidate build for default. Assuming no major / game breaking bugs are found within 2 days, this build will be promoted to default.
